  (str content) (str `[Amendment of Act 43 of 1951.]—Rep. by the Repealing and Amending Act, 2001 (30 of 2001), s. 2 and the First Schedule (w.e.f. 3-9-2001).`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_5_00036_199142_1517807323144&sectionId=39694&sectionno=8&orderno=8&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_5_00036_199142_1517807323144)
